text.tspan: Come by booth C-21 for Homebrewers and get Answers to some of the most
important Questions that could also keep You awake all Night...
- How bitter will Aronia Berries make an IPA when You use too much?
- Should an Aronia IPA come out of Balance, what Color would it have?
- Will the Sorachi Ace herbal thing clash wonderfully with Saison Yeast spiciness?
- Is dry hopping with Sorachi Ace a good Way of ruining Your Beer?
Don't worry if the Question You didn't want an Answer to is not asked -
Let's come up with Q&A Together over a Beer!
